### BOOTLOADER
+ OpenCore 0.5.6

### HOW TO INSTALL

  + download https://github.com/acidanthera/MacInfoPkg, and generate serial

  ```
  $ macserial -m iMac19,1 -n 1 # SystemSerialNumber | MLB
  C02CNSYCJV3Q | C02018101QXLNV91F

  $ uuid # SystemUUID
  bc1bf4a0-3ffc-0138-6a3f-28a159011ce8
  ```
